About White Oaks Mobile Home Park
About White Oaks Mobile Home Park
Welcome to our manufactured home community nestled in the heart of Southwest Ocala, Florida where convenience meets comfort. Situated in close proximity to shopping centers, healthcare facilities, and an array of Marion County attractions, our location ensures that you're never far from the essentials or the excitement.
Check out our listings!
Our Approach
At White Oaks Mobile Home Park, we prioritize a sense of ownership and community, which is why rentals are not available – we believe in fostering a neighborhood where residents truly feel invested in their homes and surroundings.
Our Expertise
Whether you're in the market for a brand-new manufactured home or a pre-loved gem, we offer a diverse selection to suit your preferences and budget. Worried about financing? Don't be. We work with reputable lenders to  make the home-buying experience seamless.
